the most effective regimens for treating LV-5-FU-resistant metastatic colorectal 
cancer.
CONCLUSIONS: This study shows that oxaliplatin dose intensification 
significantly improves response rate and PFS in pretreated metastatic disease 
without increasing severe toxicity.

